languages.text: "Шеренги воинов страшились взгляда Домин. Мятежи угасали по взмаху {rt_mf|его|ее} ладони. Вы — не воины. Вам не пережить {rt_mf|его|ее} взора. Помните это".
"Whole ranks of warriors have feared the Domin's gaze. Rebellions have withered at the wave of {rt_mf|his|her} hand. You are no warriors. You will not withstand {rt_mf|his|her} gaze. Remember that."

languages.text: « Des légions de guerriers ont plié sous le regard {rt_mf|du Domin|de la Domin}. Des rébellions entières ont été balayées d'un seul geste de sa main. Vous n'êtes pas des guerriers. Vous ne résisterez pas à son regard. Ne l'oubliez pas. »

languages.text: «Filas enteras de guerreros han temblado ante la mirada de{rt_mf|l| la} Domin. Numerosas rebeliones se han asfixiado tras un gesto de su mano. No sois guerreros. No podréis hacer frente a su mirada. Recordadlo».

languages.text: 「隊列全体を成す戦士たちがドミンの視線におそれを成していた。反乱軍は{rt_mf|彼|彼女}の手の一振りで委縮した。お前たちは戦士ではない。お前たちには{rt_mf|彼|彼女}の視線に耐えるなどできない。そのことを忘れるな」
languages.original_text: "Whole ranks of warriors have feared the Domin's gaze. Rebellions have withered at the wave of {rt_mf|his|her} hand. You are no warriors. You will not withstand {rt_mf|his|her} gaze. Remember that."

languages.text: “所有战士都惧怕秘者的目光。只要{rt_mf|他|她}大手一挥，所有叛乱分子都会被连根铲除。你们不是战士，你们无法抵抗{rt_mf|他|她}的目光，记住这一点。”

languages.text: "Domin'in bakışları karşısında koskoca savaşçı birlikleri dehşete düştü. Elinin bir hareketi karşısında isyanlar solup gitti. Sizler savaşçı değilsiniz. Onun bakışlarına direnemezsiniz. Bunu aklınızdan çıkarmayın."
languages.original_text: "Whole ranks of warriors have feared the Domin's gaze. Rebellions have withered at the wave of {rt_mf|his|her} hand. You are no warriors. You will not withstand {rt_mf|his|her} gaze. Remember that."
